***********************
**********安装
***********************
http://www.semantic-ui.cn/introduction/getting-started.html
-----------------------------------------------
npm install semantic-ui --save
cd semantic/
gulp build
-----------------------------------------------
***********************
*    Laravel 安装
***********************
-----------------------------------------------
npm install semantic-ui --save

路径选择../public

cd semantic/
gulp build
-----------------------------------------------

=======================================================================================
***************************************************************************************
									控件代码笔记
***************************************************************************************
=======================================================================================
***********************
**********容器
***********************
一般容器
<div class="ui container">
  <p></p>
</div>
-----------------------------------------------
文本容器
<div class="ui text container">
</div>
-----------------------------------------------
容器变种
-----------------------------------------------
文本对齐
左
<div class="ui left aligned container">
  <p></p>
</div>
中
<div class="ui center aligned container">
  <p></p>
</div>
右
<div class="ui right aligned container">
  <p></p>
</div>
适应
<div class="ui justified container">
  <p></p>
</div>
满宽
<div class="ui fluid container">
    <p></p>
</div>
=======================================================================================
***********************
**********按钮
***********************
按钮
<button class="ui button">Follow </button>
-----------------------------------------------
强调按钮
<button class="ui primary button">Save </button>
<button class="ui secondary button">Okay </button>
-----------------------------------------------
动画按钮
<div class="ui animated button" tabindex="0">
  <div class="visible content">Next</div>
  <div class="hidden content">
    <i class="right arrow icon"></i>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="ui vertical animated button" tabindex="0">
  <div class="hidden content">Shop</div>
  <div class="visible content">
    <i class="shop icon"></i>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="ui animated fade button" tabindex="0">
  <div class="visible content">Sign-up for a Pro account</div>
  <div class="hidden content">$12.99 a month </div>
</div>

visable:默认
hidden:hover
animated:指定按钮为动画按钮
tabindex:键盘Tab键选中按钮button标签自带，div标签按钮需要加这个
动画效果:
vertical
fade
-----------------------------------------------
标签按钮
<div class="ui labeled button" tabindex="0">
  <div class="ui button"><i class="heart icon"></i> Like </div>
  <a class="ui basic label">
    2,048
  </a>
</div>
<div class="ui left labeled button" tabindex="0">
  <a class="ui basic right pointing label">
    2,048
  </a>
  <div class="ui button"><i class="heart icon"></i> Like </div>
</div>
<div class="ui left labeled button" tabindex="0">
  <a class="ui basic label">
    1,048
  </a>
  <div class="ui icon button">
    <i class="fork icon"></i>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="ui labeled button" tabindex="0">
    <div class="ui red button"><i class="heart icon"></i> Like </div>
    <a class="ui basic red left pointing label">
        1,048
    </a>
</div>

ui basic label:标签部分
left/right pointing:标签小箭头
labeled:指定按钮为标签按钮
left labeled:标签在左边，默认在右边
颜色:
red
blue
pink
green
orange
-----------------------------------------------
图标按钮
<button class="ui icon button">
  <i class="cloud icon"></i>
</button>

icon:指定按钮为图标按钮
图标:
cloud
-----------------------------------------------
标签图标按钮
<button class="ui labeled icon button">
	<i class="pause icon"></i> Pause 
</button>
<button class="ui right labeled icon button">
	<i class="right arrow icon"></i> Next 
</button>

labeled icon:指定按钮为标签图标按钮
-----------------------------------------------
基本按钮
<button class="ui primary basic button">
	<i class="icon user"></i> Add Friend 
</button>

basic:指定按钮为基本按钮
强调:
primary 
secondary 
positive 
negative 
颜色:
red 
orange 
yellow 
olive 
green 
teal 
blue 
violet 
purple 
pink 
brown 
grey 
black 
-----------------------------------------------
颜色翻转高亮按钮
<button class="ui inverted red button">Red</button>
<button class="ui inverted red basic button">Basic Red</button>

inverted:指定按钮为颜色翻转高亮按钮
basic:指定仅边框变色
-----------------------------------------------
按钮组
<div class="ui buttons">
  <button class="ui button">One</button>
  <button class="ui button">Two</button>
  <button class="ui button">Three</button>
</div>

ui buttons:指定按钮组
-----------------------------------------------
图标按钮组
<div class="ui icon buttons">
    <button class="ui button"><i class="bold icon"></i></button>
    <button class="ui button"><i class="underline icon"></i></button>
    <button class="ui button"><i class="text width icon"></i></button>
</div>

icon buttons:图标按钮组
-----------------------------------------------
条件按钮
<div class="ui buttons">
  <button class="ui button">un</button>
  <div class="or" data-text="ou"></div>
  <button class="ui positive button">deux</button>
</div>

or:条件逻辑
data-text:指定条件逻辑显示文字
-----------------------------------------------
按钮状态
-----------------------------------------------
<button class="ui active button"><i class="user icon"></i> Follow </button>
<button class="ui disabled button"><i class="user icon"></i> Followed </button>
<button class="ui loading button">Loading</button>

active:激活状态
disabled:禁用状态
loading:等待状态
-----------------------------------------------
按钮变体
-----------------------------------------------
<button class="ui facebook button"><i class="facebook icon"></i> Facebook </button>
<button class="ui twitter button"><i class="twitter icon"></i> Twitter </button>
<button class="ui google plus button"><i class="google plus icon"></i> Google Plus </button>
<button class="ui vk button"><i class="vk icon"></i> VK </button>
<button class="ui linkedin button"><i class="linkedin icon"></i> LinkedIn </button>
<button class="ui instagram button"><i class="instagram icon"></i> Instagram </button>
<button class="ui youtube button"><i class="youtube icon"></i> YouTube </button>

变体属性:
facebook
twitter
google
vk
linkedin
linkedin
youtube
-----------------------------------------------
按钮尺寸
-----------------------------------------------
<button class="huge ui button">Huge </button>

尺寸属性:
mini 
tiny 
small 
medium 
large 
big 
huge 
massive 
-----------------------------------------------
按钮浮动
<button class="ui right floated button">Right Floated</button>
<button class="ui left floated button">Left Floated</button>

floated:指定浮动按钮
浮动方向:
right
left
-----------------------------------------------
按钮紧凑化
<button class="compact ui button">Hold </button>
<button class="ui compact icon button">
  <i class="pause icon"></i>
</button>
<button class="ui compact labeled icon button"><i class="pause icon"></i> Pause </button>

compact:紧凑化按钮
-----------------------------------------------
开关按钮
<button class="ui toggle button">Vote</button>

-----------------------------------------------
圆按钮
<button class="circular ui icon button">
  <i class="icon settings"></i>
</button>

circular:指定圆按钮
-----------------------------------------------
满宽按钮
<button class="fluid ui button">Fits container</button>

fluid:指定满宽按钮
-----------------------------------------------
垂直紧贴按钮
<div class="ui top attached button" tabindex="0">Top</div>
<div class="ui attached segment">
    <p>hello world</p>
</div>
<div class="ui bottom attached button" tabindex="0">Bottom</div>

<div class="ui two top attached buttons">
    <div class="ui button">One</div>
    <div class="ui button">Two</div>
</div>
<div class="ui attached segment">
    <p>hello world!</p>
</div>
<div class="ui two bottom attached buttons">
    <div class="ui button">One</div>
    <div class="ui button">Two</div>
</div>

attached:指定紧贴按钮
按钮组情况按钮个数:
two
three
four
紧贴方向:
top
bottom
-----------------------------------------------
水平紧贴按钮
<button class="ui left attached button">Left</button>
<button class="right attached ui button">Right</button>

紧贴方向:
left
right
-----------------------------------------------
垂直按钮组
<div class="ui vertical buttons">
  <button class="ui button">动态</button>
  <button class="ui button">Messages</button>
  <button class="ui button">Events</button>
  <button class="ui button">Photos</button>
</div>

vertical:指定垂直按钮组
-----------------------------------------------
自由组合按钮组
<div class="ui buttons">
  <button class="ui labeled icon button"><i class="left chevron icon"></i> Back </button>
  <button class="ui button"><i class="stop icon"></i> Stop </button>
  <button class="ui right labeled icon button">Forward <i class="right chevron icon"></i> </button>
</div>
