=======================================================================================
***********************
**********标题
***********************
普通标题
<h1 class="ui header">First header</h1>
<h2 class="ui header">Second header</h2>
<h3 class="ui header">Third header</h3>
<h4 class="ui header">Fourth header</h4>
<h5 class="ui header">Fifth header</h5>

header:指定标题
-----------------------------------------------
图标标题
<h2 class="ui icon header">
  <i class="settings circular icon"></i>
  <div class="content">Account Settings <div class="sub header">Manage your account settings and set e-mail preferences.</div>
  </div>
</h2>

icon header:图标标题
circular:指定原先图标标题
-----------------------------------------------
子标题
<h2 class="ui sub header">Price </h2>
<span>$10.99</span>

ui sub header:指定子标题
-----------------------------------------------
图片标题
<h2 class="ui header">
    <img class="ui image" src="/logo.png">
    <div class="content">Learn More </div>
</h2>
<h2 class="ui header">
    <img class="ui circular image" src="/logo.png">
    <div class="content">Learn More </div>
</h2>

ui image:图片
circular:圆形图片
-----------------------------------------------
不可用标题
<div class="ui disabled header">Disabled Header </div>

disabled:指定不可用标题
-----------------------------------------------
标题分割线
<h3 class="ui dividing header">Dividing Header </h3>

dividing:指定分割线
-----------------------------------------------
区域块标题
<h3 class="ui block header">Block Header </h3>

ui block header:指定区域块标题
-----------------------------------------------
紧贴标题
<h3 class="ui top attached header">Top Attached </h3>
<div class="ui attached segment">
  <p></p>
</div>
<h3 class="ui attached header">Attached </h3>
<div class="ui attached segment">
  <p></p>
</div>
<h3 class="ui bottom attached header">Bottom Attached </h3>

ui attached header:指定津贴标题
紧贴位置(默认为文段中紧贴):
top
bottom
-----------------------------------------------
浮动标题
<div class="ui clearing segment">
  <h3 class="ui right floated header">Go Forward </h3>
  <h3 class="ui left floated header">Go Back </h3>
</div>

floated:指定浮动标题
浮动方向:
right
right
-----------------------------------------------
文本对齐
<div class="ui segment">
    <h3 class="ui right aligned header">Right </h3>
    <h3 class="ui left aligned header">Left </h3>
    <h3 class="ui justified header">This should take up the full width even if only one line </h3>
    <h3 class="ui center aligned header">Center </h3>
</div>

aligned:文本对齐
对其方向:
right
left
justified
center
