***********************
**********图片
***********************
普通图片
<img class="ui small image" src="/logo.png">

<div class="ui small image">
  <img src="/images/wireframe/image.png">
</div>

<div class="ui small image">
  <svg width="150" height="150">
    <image xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="/images/wireframe/image.png" x="0" y="0" width="100%" height="100%"></image>
  </svg>
</div>

ui small image:指定图片
-----------------------------------------------
图片链接
<a href="http://google.com" class="ui medium image">
  <img src="/images/wireframe/image-text.png">
</a>

hidden:隐藏
-----------------------------------------------
隐藏图片
<img class="hidden ui image" src="/images/wireframe/image.png">

hidden:隐藏
-----------------------------------------------
头像图片
<img class="ui avatar image" src="/images/wireframe/square-image.png">
<span>Username</span>

avatar:指定头像图片
-----------------------------------------------
图片边框
<img class="ui medium bordered image" src="/logo.png">

bordered:指定边框
-----------------------------------------------
全宽图片
<img class="ui fluid image" src="/images/wireframe/image.png">

bordered:指定全宽
-----------------------------------------------
圆角图片
<img class="ui medium rounded image" src="/logo.png">

rounded:指定圆角图片
-----------------------------------------------
圆形图片
<img class="ui medium circular image" src="/logo.png">

circular:指定圆形图片
-----------------------------------------------
图片组纵排
<img class="ui top aligned tiny image" src="/logo.png">
<span>Top Aligned</span>
<div class="ui divider"></div>
<img class="ui middle aligned tiny image" src="/logo.png">
<span>Middle Aligned</span>
<div class="ui divider"></div>
<img class="ui bottom aligned tiny image" src="/logo.png">
<span>Bottom Aligned</span>

aligned:指定排列
排列位置:
top
middle
bottom
-----------------------------------------------
图片居中
<img class="ui centered medium image" src="/images/wireframe/image.png">

centered:图片居中
-----------------------------------------------
图片排列文字中
<img class="ui mini spaced image" src="/images/wireframe/image.png">

spaced:图片排列文字中
-----------------------------------------------
图片排列文字中
<img class="ui mini spaced image" src="/images/wireframe/image.png">

spaced:图片排列文字中
-----------------------------------------------
图片浮动
<img class="ui small left floated image" src="/images/wireframe/text-image.png">

floated:环绕浮动
-----------------------------------------------
图片尺寸

Class Name	Size
mini		35px
tiny		80px
small		150px
medium		300px
large		450px
big			600px
huge		800px
massive		960px
-----------------------------------------------
图片组
<div class="ui tiny images">
  <img class="ui image" src="/images/wireframe/image.png">
  <img class="ui image" src="/images/wireframe/image.png">
  <img class="ui image" src="/images/wireframe/image.png">
  <img class="ui image" src="/images/wireframe/image.png">
</div>

ui images:指定图片组
=======================================================================================
***********************
********输入框
***********************
输入框
<div class="ui input">
  <input type="text" placeholder="Search...">
</div>

ui input:指定输入框
-----------------------------------------------
输入框状态
<div class="ui input focus">
  <input type="text" placeholder="Search...">
</div>

状态:
focus
loading
disabled 
error
-----------------------------------------------
图标输入框
<div class="ui icon input">
  <input type="text" placeholder="Search...">
  <i class="search icon"></i>
</div>

ui icon input:指定图标输入框
图标位置:
left
right
-----------------------------------------------
标签输入框
<div class="ui labeled input">
    <div class="ui label">http:// </div>
    <input type="text" placeholder="mysite.com">
</div>

ui labeled input:指定标签输入框
ui label:标签
-----------------------------------------------
透明输入框
<div class="ui transparent input">
  <input type="text" placeholder="Search...">
</div>

transparent：透明
-----------------------------------------------
输入框尺寸
<div class="ui mini icon input">
  <input type="text" placeholder="Search mini...">
  <i class="search icon"></i>
</div>

尺寸:
mini 
small 
large 
big 
huge 
massive 
