ui labels:指定标签组
=======================================================================================
***********************
********列表
***********************
一般列表
<div class="ui list">
  <div class="item">
  </div>
  <div class="item">
  </div>
  <div class="item">
  </div>
  <div class="item">
  </div>
</div>

ui list:列表
item:列表项

简单版
<ul class="ui list">
  <li>Gaining Access</li>
  <li>Inviting Friends</li>
  <li>Benefits <ul>
      <li>Use Anywhere</li>
      <li>Rebates</li>
      <li>Discounts</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Warranty</li>
</ul>
-----------------------------------------------
排列列表
<div class="ui ordered list">
  <a class="item">Getting Started</a>
  <a class="item">Introduction</a>
  <div class="item">
    <a>Languages</a>
    <div class="list">
      <a class="item">HTML</a>
      <a class="item">Javascript</a>
      <a class="item">CSS</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a class="item">Review</a>
</div>

ordered:排列列表

简单版
<ol class="ui list">
  <li>Signing Up</li>
  <li>User Benefits</li>
  <li>User Types <ol>
      <li>Admin</li>
      <li>Power User</li>
      <li>Regular User</li>
    </ol>
  </li>
  <li>Deleting Your Account</li>
</ol>
-----------------------------------------------
指定列表头字符
<ol class="ui list">
  <li value="*">Signing Up</li>
  <li value="*">User Benefits</li>
  <li value="*">User Types <ol>
      <li value="-">Admin</li>
      <li value="-">Power User</li>
      <li value="-">Regular User</li>
    </ol>
  </li>
  <li value="*">Deleting Your Account</li>
</ol>

value:指定列表前符号
-----------------------------------------------
连接列表
<div class="ui link list">
  <div class="active item">Home</div>
  <a class="item">About</a>
  <a class="item">Jobs</a>
  <a class="item">Team</a>
</div>

ui link list:指定连接列表
-----------------------------------------------
动画列表
<div class="ui middle aligned animated relaxed list">
    <div class="item">
        <img class="ui avatar image" src="/logo.png">
        <div class="content">
            <div class="header">Helen</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
        <img class="ui avatar image" src="/logo.png">
        <div class="content">
            <div class="header">Christian</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
        <img class="ui avatar image" src="/logo.png">
        <div class="content">
            <div class="header">Daniel</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

ui animated list:动画列表
top aligned:文字上对齐
middle aligned:文字垂直居中
bottom aligned:文字下对齐
relaxed:松散项间距
-----------------------------------------------
列表分割线
<div class="ui middle aligned animated divided list">
    <div class="item">
        <img class="ui avatar image" src="/logo.png">
        <div class="content">
            <div class="header">Helen</div>
        </div>
    </div>
